00:27:25,910 --> 00:27:30,230
If you can't bring me results in that time, prepare to lose your job.

369
00:27:33,950 --> 00:27:36,110
Leo.

370
00:27:39,470 --> 00:27:42,960
Leo... How did he bring Leo?

371
00:27:42,960 --> 00:27:46,470
Right? Does he know someone?

372
00:27:46,470 --> 00:27:48,270
Oh, right. I can't be sitting here.

373
00:27:48,270 --> 00:27:51,510
I'll contact you guys later.

374
00:27:51,510 --> 00:27:53,750
The file, the file.

