00:28:03,290 --> 00:28:05,940
Chairman, it's so good to see you like this.

378
00:28:05,940 --> 00:28:08,520
Chairman, it's been so long since you saw Leo.

379
00:28:08,520 --> 00:28:11,280
How about a picture?

380
00:28:11,280 --> 00:28:14,470
Look here! Leo, look here!

381
00:28:14,470 --> 00:28:17,660
Taking the picture!

382
00:28:20,080 --> 00:28:22,920
