00:28:26,140 --> 00:28:29,320
That bitch wouldn't have let you take Leo so easily.

384
00:28:29,320 --> 00:28:32,380
How did you manage to bring him? By chance,

385
00:28:32,380 --> 00:28:34,690
you didn't kidnap him, right?

