00:29:16,990 --> 00:29:18,970
- Chairman. 
- Go ahead.

396
00:29:18,970 --> 00:29:24,260
Is Classification Chief the reason you were left out of the parole list?

397
00:29:24,260 --> 00:29:27,010
Yes. It's a done deal with the warden,

398
00:29:27,010 --> 00:29:30,710
